{"tid":1653462,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（有真核彈無理由唔用）15/10 星期二晚 Now新聞台樓下 燈光晚會 聲援被黑警毒打now採訪車車長","createTime":"2019-10-14T05:43:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-14T07:32:33.000Z","uid":36494,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"cf9965430d563153892493fcc707a2d3dbfcc237","tid":1653462,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T05:43:52.000Z","msg":"日期：15/10<br />\n時間：晚上8時<br />\n地點：Now新聞台樓下（灣仔電訉大廈）<br />\n<br />\n和平聚會，一齊用手提電話燈光，聲援被毒打now新聞採訪車車長<br />\n<br />\n點解要做：<br />\n1.connect新聞界，一齊對抗警暴<br />\n2.提供多啲報導材料，等傳媒做尻黑警<br />\n3.呢個有曬新聞片，受害人身份，仲要係新聞工作者，係真真正正的核彈"},{"pid":"92c035ee15c311545224f6cdec8bc602143ce853","tid":1653462,"uid":209543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T05:44:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5cb50f44e63960186a63929041b2d31e0536a008","tid":1653462,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T05:44:28.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"b6d82222ef689f80d3ba7a8084cb8456d1d773f0","tid":1653462,"uid":209543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T05:44:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dd61532ae2bdba02c657057284f4157413c4c735","tid":1653462,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T05:44:38.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"10787f4f27c17bbda0a313f2e21191275c6d03e5","tid":1653462,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T05:44:49.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"c376ed8df3984d38452e5c4e1fb52533a41693df","tid":1653462,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T05:44:59.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"c0464f39909fb1eae4d620863f78f6cf658ac0bf","tid":1653462,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T05:45:09.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"f8244d9c095782303902413e0910c84e7d04f66b","tid":1653462,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T05:45:19.000Z","msg":"6/10"